{"type": "article", "id": 12387, "title": "Yamagiwa 赖特风格台灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-21T07:42:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122509quXV3dIr8SJvPwKo.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自日本的 Yamagiwa 公司推出了一款新的台灯，其设计原型是弗兰克•劳埃德•赖特为美国威斯康星州设计的塔里埃森剧院。在台灯里面，他们使用了赖特最喜欢的颜色红色作为台灯的主体方块颜色，红色的色块看上去非常迷人，三个灯箱都可以散发光芒，被方向板分散，柔和静谧，在各种背景下几乎都可以和环境融为一体。这是<a href=\"http://www.yamagiwa.co.jp/global/\" target=\"_blank\">Yamagiwa 工作室的主页</a>，可以查看其更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261401429iFzd2p0qCOPcW5r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78606357\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140143CVpkFvscDHjLGWUI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75183374\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261401431JSwaR2Uh3je0Ksu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79095355\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140144wu1WnGriPbgYkq85.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261401447qCOTAPNlzuf6jJF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140145kZ5F9hNnfm3wlbKj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140145DaiPvT9Nsfm8cykS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<span></span>\n\n\n\n"}